Rock Paper Scisscors Planning!

When I choose Paper
  If computer chose Rock
    I get 1 point
  else if the computer chose scissors
    the computer gets 1 point
  else the computer chose paper as well and it's a tie
  
When I choose Rock
  If computer chose Scissors
    I get 1 point
  else if the computer chose Paper
    the computer gets 1 point 
  else the computer chose Rock as well and it's a tie
  
When I choose Scissors
  If computer chose Paper
    I get 1 point
  else if the computer chose Rock
    the computer gets 1 point
  else the computer chose Scissors as well and it's a tie
